As a visitor:
	- I want to view all products (index)
	- I want to view details of each product (show)
			- price
			- description
			- reviews
			- picture
		(So that the user is knowledgeable about their product) 
	- I want to sign up and become a user

As a user:
	- I want to write reviews for products I have purchased

As an admin:
	- I want to be able to add products
	- I want to be able to delete products
	- I want to be able to edit products